/* Regarding the Recent Removal of a Citation on the page Etron Technology, Inc. */ new section

These two websites cited, as well as the content included, are extremely unreliable and biased. The websites are not credible and are backed up by technology companies of possibly the subject's competitiors. Please do not add them back, thankyou.

The deleted statement was overly dramatic. Language used in the linked source is also overly dramatic, and may be results of business and commerical influence. The linked source was also poorly sourced and cited, and has absolutely zero references on where the data were obtained from. I believe such business coverage should not appear on a wikipedia page. Please put it back if you do not think the way I think it is, thankyou!
